35767.title: The Decade the Rich Won
35767.description: This programme follows the sequence of events as the British government and the Bank of England are forced to react to the economic shocks brought on by Brexit and Covid-19.

35799.title: The Decade the Rich Won
35799.description: In the last episode of the series, as the British prime minister Theresa May struggles to implement Brexit, wealth inequality is increasing - sparking anger and protests.
